snippet.title: SynthMania
snippet.description:
Hello, I'm Paolo Di Nicolantonio of SynthMania. In this channel you can find videos of synthesizers and many other types of musical and electronic gear.

PLEASE NOTE: The email below is for business inquiries. Please don't email me at the address below with questions related to synth or music. Please ask those questions in the comment section of each video. Thank you
